## Commands

| Task | Command |
|---|---|
| Dev server | `make run` |
| Tests | `make test` (fast) / `make test-all` |
| Lint / format | `make lint` / `make format` |
| Types | `make typecheck` |
| Migrations | `make makemigrations && make migrate` |
