## Architecture

`data/` (models) → `domain/` (operations / queries / processes) → `interfaces/` (portal / api / backoffice{% if use_celery %} / tasks{% endif %}).
Layering is enforced by ruff + import-linter (`make lint`) — see `CLAUDE.md` for the full rules.

## Deploy

{% if deploy_tier == "docker" %}Docker compose + Fabric: `fab deploy` (see `fabfile.py`; configure host via env vars `DEPLOY_HOST`, `DEPLOY_USER`, `DEPLOY_PATH`).{% else %}VPS systemd + gunicorn + nginx: edit the variables at the top of `deploy.sh` and run it on the server.{% endif %}
